<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10698092>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Maximum-likelihood tree generated with the K2 + G + I model from the SSU rDNA sequence alignment. The scale bar represents the number of substitutions per site units. In clades the first value corresponds to the bootstrap value calculated using the K2 + G + I model and the second value corresponds to the bootstrap value calculated using the GTR + G + I model. Newly obtained sequences are indicated in boldface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10698092/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

